      "rationale": "Validation performed on the FDA generic centrifugal pump, which is the same platform as the COU device. Operating conditions overlap with clinical CPB envelope. Geometric fidelity of the validation model matches the COU model. Note: validation fluid was a Newtonian glycerol-water analogue or Newtonian-treated porcine blood; the impact of the non-Newtonian rheology exclusion on relevance was considered informally during model development but is not documented in a fidelity trade study, and no validation activity specifically tests the Newtonian assumption."
