      "rationale": "SST k-omega turbulence model selected based on published benchmark comparisons for rotating-passage flows. Giersiepen-Wurzinger power-law hemolysis model selected; coefficients from Zhang et al. (2011) recalibration. Model form uncertainty estimated at ±18% based on literature spread of hemolysis model coefficients. Non-Newtonian constitutive form was considered as an alternative during model scoping; the decision to retain the Newtonian assumption was noted in project records as acceptable given the high-shear operating regime, but no quantitative fidelity trade study was conducted and no sensitivity analysis result is linked to this assessment."
